Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takato.{Takato.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nevěřím tomu.{I don't believe it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne, byl to jen sen.{No, that was a dream.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muselo se mi to zdát. \NAle neříkej mi, že…{It must've been a dream.\NBut don't tell me he…}
